data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought after Brewerytown neighborhood! This stunning property offers the perfect combination of modern features and old-world charm. Step inside and be greeted by an open concept living room and dining room, complete with beautiful hardwood flooring, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones.  The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting sleek stainless steel appliances and ample space for culinary creativity. The exposed brick adds a touch of character and leads you to the second floor where you'll find three spacious bedrooms, each adorned with wall-to-wall carpeting for ultimate comfort. A full bath completes this level, providing convenience and privacy for all.  Step outside and discover your own private oasis – a cement patio and a fenced-in backyard. Imagine hosting barbecues, gardening, or simply enjoying your morning coffee in this peaceful outdoor space. With central air and heat, you'll stay comfortable all year round, no matter the weather.  Location, location, location! This home is perfectly situated close to public transportation, making commuting a breeze. With easy access to I-76, I-676, I-95, PA Rt. 1, and PA-611, you'll have quick routes to wherever you need to go. Within 15-20 minutes, you can reach Center City, Sports Arenas, and Philadelphia International airport, allowing you to take advantage of all the cultural and entertainment opportunities that the city has to offer.  In addition to the convenience, this neighborhood offers fantastic shopping options and access to Fairmount Park and the Museum District. Whether you're a nature enthusiast or an art lover, you'll never be far from your favorite activities.  Don't miss the chance to make this house your forever home. With its ideal location, charming features, and unbeatable amenities, it truly has it all. Schedule a showing today and envision yourself living your best life in this Brewerytown gem!
